=== Scenario 3: Multiple Checks During 1 Second ===

note over Loop
  Timeline of job checking in 1 second
end note

Loop -> Tracker: Initialize at t=0
activate Tracker

Loop -> Loop: t=0ms: start
note over Loop: ~4 checks per second\n(every 250ms)
Loop -> Tracker: t=250ms: check 1
Loop -> Tracker: t=500ms: check 2
Loop -> Tracker: t=750ms: check 3
Loop -> Tracker: t=1000ms: check 4

note right of Loop
  **Frequency Analysis:**
  - Period: 250ms
  - Frequency: 4 checks/second
  - Duration of each check: <1ms (fast path)
  - With jobs: 1-5ms (write lock acquisition)
  - Overhead: ~4-20ms per second (1-2% of CPU)

  **Comparison:**
  - Per-event checking: 100+ checks/sec during typing
  - Periodic checking: 4 checks/sec always
  - Improvement: 25x fewer lock acquisitions
end note

